content.rendered: Pusat kamera CCTV HiLook, kami menyediakan Paket CCTV 8 Channel 8 Channel Ultimate IP untuk anda dengan harga murah. Anda dapat memantau kegiatan / aktivitas sehari-hari dengan jarak jauh secara real time. Kamera HiLook 8 Channel Ultimate IP mempunyai:2.0 MP Network PT Camera Up to 2.0 megapixel high resolution Two video streams 2.8mm fixed lens Digital Wide Dynamic Range 3D Digital Noise Reduction Built-in microphone and speaker, support two-way audio Support on-board storage, up to 128GB Up to 5 m IR range Built-in Wi-Fi 5 VDC ± 10 %, micro USB interface Mobile Monitoring via Hik-Connect
